value.0: This warrior scout, a member of the Raiders, is off duty.

This lithe creature has a head resembling a cross between a panther and a human's face, with distinct whiskers poking out of slighlty puffy cheecks. The body is sinewy and flexible, and ends in powerful cat's paws. It tends to stay away from direct main combat, and instead you hear it speaking in an oddly human voice, calling down Druidic magics upon you. It is clearly a lycanthrope of some sort, probably a panther or a jaguar.
